high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the pot on the stove.
Pick the pot up off of the stove.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn the water on and then off, and then take the pot out of the sink.
Go right and stand in front of the stove.
Put the pot on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean put on the stove.

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room and turn to face the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn left, cross the room and turn to face the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn on the water and wash the pot.
Turn right, cross the room and turn left to face the stove.
Put the pot on the left rear burner.
anns.task_desc: Wash the pot and return it to the stove.

high_descs: Turn to your left and cross the room to the stove on your left
Pick up the pot that is on the stove
Turn around and cross the room to the sink that is on your right
Place the pot into the sink and turn on the faucet.  Turn off the faucet and pick up the pot.
Turn right and cross the room to the stove on your left
Place the pot on the back left burner on the stove
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pot on a stove.
